The paper also discusses privacy and security concerns related to data breaches, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of anonymized data also involves database management, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses the use of differential privacy, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
